"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":295,"aggregated":"/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/chagatai/workspace/kurultai-reflections-ui-design.md\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/chagatai/workspace/reflections-ui-implementation-summary.md\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/chagatai/workspace/reflections-ui-enhancement-complete.md\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/chagatai/workspace/kurultai-reflections-ui-implementation-status.md\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/chagatai/workspace/reflection-tracker-design.md\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/temujin/workspace/exportable-reflection-reports-design.md\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/temujin/workspace/session-reflections-frontend-design.md\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/ogedei/workspace/reflection-gap-fix-2026-03-07.md\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/docs/reflection-pipeline-reference.md\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/kurultai-reflection-2026-03-04-1702.md\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/kurultai-reflection-2026-03-04-0211.md\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/reflections/2026-03-05-1802-hourly-reflection.md\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/reflections/2026-03-06-0802-hourly-reflection.md\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/reflections/2026-03-06-0703-hourly-reflection.md\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/reflections/2026-03-06-0102-hourly-reflection.md\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/reflections/2026-03-05-2002-hourly-reflection.md\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/reflections/2026-03-06-0602-hourly-reflection.md\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/reflections/2026-03-07-0704-hourly-reflection.md\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/reflections/2026-03-05-1203-hourly-reflection.md\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/reflections/2026-03-05-1702-hourly-reflection.md","cwd":"/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772913767248}}
